Potential skit:

[quote:2c2m8ofp]Guy knocks on a door and it's opened by two men. The guy says &quot;I'm here to join the Monty Python Elitism Club.&quot;

1st man says, &quot;the club, eh?&quot;

2nd man says, &quot;okay, let's see you quote every line from the Dead Parrot sketch.&quot;

The guy does.

1st man says, &quot;not bad.&quot;

2nd man says, &quot;yes, but before we decide, you'll also have to do a silly walk.&quot;

The guy does, though not without some difficulty.

1st man says, &quot;hmmm... passable I guess.&quot;

2nd man says, &quot;here, slap yourself in the face with this dead fish.&quot;

The guy sighs but, dutifully, slaps himself in the face several times with the dead fish.

1st man says, &quot;ha, that was good.&quot;

2nd man says, &quot;I'll agree with that.&quot;

The guy says, &quot;so... can I can the Monty Python Elitism Club?&quot;

1st man says, &quot;what are you asking us for?&quot;

2nd man says, &quot;it's next door.&quot;

The door is closed.

The guy stands there looking dejected until a knight walks along and hits him on the head with a chicken.[/quote:2c2m8ofp]
